1
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:11,000
Mami!

2
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:17,000
Oči!

3
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Binka!

4
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:26,000
Brina!

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,700
No, zato bom pa napisala pismo vili straniščki.

6
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:32,500
No, le tako dosežeš, da se kaj spremeni.

7
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:33,860
Oranžna luč, oči.

8
00:00:33,860 --> 00:00:36,000
Ops!

9
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:37,150
Oči!

10
00:00:37,150 --> 00:00:38,700
Zapeljal si skozi oranžno luč!

11
00:00:38,700 --> 00:00:40,650
Ja, ja, pa res.

12
00:00:40,650 --> 00:00:42,999
Je nisi videl?

13
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:43,400
Ja, sem jo.

14
00:00:43,400 --> 00:00:46,500
A pri oranžni zmanjšaš hitrost in ustaviš.

15
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:49,300
Zakaj nisi upočasnil in ustavil?

16
00:00:49,300 --> 00:00:53,350
Ah, no, poseben primer je bil.

